get.description:
SSE stream of new alerts for the current org.

Frontend usage:
    const es = new EventSource('/api/v1/alerts/stream', { withCredentials: true });
    es.addEventListener('alert', e => { const data = JSON.parse(e.data); ... });

AgentStreamConfig.description:
Where the agent should publish its camera streams (cloud topology).

push_enabled=False means MediaMTX pulls cameras directly (local/on-LAN);
the agent does NOT push and runs no ffmpeg relays.
